OL,6,FBereaved families have gathered
OL,7,Foutside HMP Parc in following nine
OL,8,Fsudden deaths at the prison since the
OL,9,Fend of February.
OL,11,FSecurity firm has managed the prison
OL,12,Fsince it opened in 1997 and it
OL,13,Freceived a 10-year contract to
OL,14,Fcontinue operating it in 2022.
OL,16,FA spokesperson said that HMP Parc 'has
OL,17,Ffor a long time had a good reputation
OL,18,Fas a safe and decent prison',
OL,19,Faccording to the last inspection by
OL,20,Fthe Chief Inspector of Prisons.
