OL,6,FFrances Jones' nephew Mikey, 19, died
OL,7,Fat the prison just less than three
OL,8,Fweeks ago after struggling with
OL,9,Faddiction and had been recently
OL,10,Frecalled to prison. He took his own
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FShe told ITV Wales: "Where were (the
OL,14,Fprison guards)? He was on (suicide)
OL,15,Fwatch. Why was it that he was allowed
OL,16,Fto die?
OL,18,F"We can't stand here and say Mikey had
OL,19,Fdone it to get any sort of help. We
OL,20,Fcan't say that because we weren't
OL,21,Fthere.
