OL,6,F"But what we can say is, Mikey came in
OL,7,Fto do his time after doing his crime
OL,8,Fand he came out in a black bag. And
OL,9,Fthat is wrong. That is so, so wrong.
OL,11,F"He's been let down and so have the
OL,12,Fothers who have unluckily passed here."
OL,14,FFrances, and many of the other
OL,15,Fprotestors, are calling for to lose
OL,16,Ftheir contract to run the prison which
OL,17,Fis set to expire in 2032.
