OL,6,FShe said: "We want justice. We want
OL,7,Fthese people () out. We want the
OL,8,FGovernment to come in and take back
OL,9,Fcontrol. At least we'll know that
OL,10,F(inmates) will have the protection
OL,11,Fthey deserve."
OL,13,FWhen questioned about the HMP Parc in
OL,14,Fthe House of Commons, UK Prisons
OL,15,FMinister acknowledged there were some
OL,16,Fchallenges around security and
OL,17,Frecruiting experienced staff but
OL,18,Frejected calls for the Government to
OL,19,Ftake over saying the prison is being
OL,20,F"well-run".
